data.description: This home offers a highly desirable layout and is just minutes from I-69 and downtown Bloomington. The current owners really appreciate the close proximity to the Clear Creek Trail.  The 9' ceilings and strategically placed windows make the space feel even larger. On the main level the family room flows into the living room and kitchen.  The kitchen features a large walk in pantry. Just off the breakfast area is a large screened in covered porch with 3 ceiling fans that overlooks the fenced back yard. This truly is an all season room thanks to the custom removable vinyl inserts. Upstairs, the primary bedroom features TWO walk-in closets, double sinks, garden tub, separate shower, and a toilet room. The additional generously sized bedrooms feature walk-in closets as well. The best part, the laundry room is located upstairs! Updates include, roof 2021, LVP 2022 and newer water heater. If you enjoy gardening, you will appreciate the raised garden beds.
